  body
    #wrapper
      #header
        span.header-item A project of Advocacy Commons
      #padded_wrapper
        #content
          noscript
            span#no_js_warning
              br
              | It looks like you have JavaScript disabled.  You'll need it to use this site.  
              a(href='http://enable-javascript.com/', target='_blank') Here
              |  are some instructions.
          #form_title_container
            #form_title Stop Rex Tillerson
          #form_container
            form#caller_data
              ul#main_form_elements
                li
                  input#email_address(type='text', placeholder='Email address', data-parsley-required, data-parsley-type='email', data-parsley-type-message='Please enter a valid email address.')
                li
                  input#postal_code(type='text', placeholder='ZIP code', data-parsley-required, data-parsley-zipcode)
                li
                  input#phone_number(type='text', placeholder='Cell phone', data-parsley-required, data-parsley-type='digits', data-parsley-type-message='Please enter numbers only.')
                li
                  input#sms_opt_in_checkbox(type='checkbox')
                  label#sms_opt_in_label(for='sms_opt_in_checkbox')
                    |  I'd like to receive mobile action alerts to stop Trump nominees. Msg & data rates may apply. You may opt out at any time. 
                    a#terms_link(href='javascript:;') Terms & Conditions
                    | .
                li
                  input#given_name(type='text', placeholder='First name')
                li
                  input#family_name(type='text', placeholder='Last name')
                li
                  input#main_submit(type='submit', value="Let's go!")
                li#email_subscription_controls
                  a#reveal_email_subscription_preferences(href='javascript:;') Edit subscription preferences
                  #email_subscription_preferences
                    input#email_opt_in_check(type='checkbox', checked='true')
                    label#email_opt_in_label(for='email_opt_in_check') Opt me in to rapid-response action alerts from Advocacy Commons.
          #meta_form
            #script.after-submit-reveal
              p
                strong
                  | Text TRex to 698-66 or call 1-888-407-1644 to be automatically connected to your Senators.
                |  To be connected to your second Senator, please text TRex again, or call the same number a second time.
              p Call script:
              blockquote
                em
                  p
                    | Hi, my name is ____, and I am your constituent calling from _____. I am calling to urge Senator ____ to vote against the nomination of Rex Tillerson for Secretary of State.
                  p
                    | Tillerson has no background or experience in foreign policy, but he does have decades of experience in making business alliances with Russia and other repressive regimes, and undermining US and international sanctions against Iran. That's not what America stands for and he should not be confirmed.
            #sharing.after-submit-reveal
              p
                em Help us build a powerful rapid-response network.
              #share_widgets_container
                #fb_share_container.share-container                  .fb-share-button(data-href='http://www.advocacycommons.org/call/tillerson-senate', data-layout='button', data-size='large', data-mobile-iframe='true')
                    a.fb-xfbml-parse-ignore(target='_blank', href='https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.advocacycommons.org%2Fcall%2Ftillerson-senate&src=sdkpreparse') Share
                #tw_share_container.share-container
                  a.twitter-share-button(href='https://twitter.com/share', data-size='large', data-text='The Senate has started debate on Rex Tillerson. Tell your Senator to vote NO.', data-show-count='false') Tweet
                  script(async='', src='//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js', charset='utf-8')
            #form_teaser
              p
                | The Senate will be voting on the nomination of Rex Tillerson at 2:30 pm ET today!  Every Senator &ndash; Democrat and Republican &ndash; needs to hear from their constituents NOW demanding that they vote NO! 
                a#show_full_form_desc(href='javascript:;') (show full description)
            #form_full_desc
              p
                | Remember: we can drive more &quot;No&quot; votes on Tillerson than any Secretary of State since at least World War II.
              p
                | To call your senators, fill in the form and use the sample script that appears on the next page to urge them to oppose Tillerson.  Be sure to check the box below your cellphone number to receive action alerts on other nominees.
              p
                | And after you've made your calls, please share this page far and wide through Facebook, Twitter and email.
